themes: recognition of organizational history and growth
key_phrases: Funding decisions should be made with input from community members
organizations with a documented history of events/performances that are showing growth
award smaller awards to a greater number of organizations rather than larger awards to fewer organizations
barriers_identified: lack of community input in funding decisions
solutions_proposed: Include community members familiar with the Austin arts and culture scene in funding decisions
Prioritize organizations with a documented history and growth in turnout
Distribute smaller awards to more organizations rather than larger awards to fewer
